Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.19,TVevaTNR,,0000,0000,0000,,Chị cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.64,TVevaTNR,,0000,0000,0000,,Tuyệt thật!
